      • handlePointInput

        public void handlePointInput(Point point)
        The method attempts to move the player to point selected in the UI.

        The method is called by the user interface. The method subsequently calls update() to initiate redrawing the map view.

        Parameters:
        point - Map point selected by player in the interface.
